      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BULLEMOR BANNER (1) had been racing in honest fashion recording two placings in a row before finishing fourth (22.32) at this track latest. Has a good record at this journey. Goes well out of this box with a win and two minor placings. Has ability and looks hard to stop. BLACK FALCON (3) has been hard to follow lately, running seventh (22.35) last time but prior to that ran very well when placed at this track. This looks easier and expected to improve sharply. COLONEL'S DREAM (2) boasts strong form at this course and distance having won four times from seven starts. Missed the frame latest (24.29) when sixth over 407m at Rockhampton in a Grade 4/5. Looks well placed here and among the chances. HOLLY MAGIC (7) gets a chance to improve on an unplaced run at her latest outing at this circuit.",
